race.comment: RAPIDO NINJA (2) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (30.01) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 520m. Got the money at his only try from this box. Looks the one to beat. PAM KEEPING (5) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 5 lengths from the winner (30.35). Returns to favourable track. Expected to run well. FERNDALE FLYER (1) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (30.34) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to be in this for a long way. SOPHIE KEEPING (3) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.
